---
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Films and visual stories by Smooth Corner Studio. Story-led video, honest moments and thoughtful visual storytelling by Daniel Pasqualini."
		/>
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Films and Visual Stories | Smooth Corner Studio</title>
	</head>

	<body>
		<header class="page-header">
			<a class="back-link" href="/#work">Back to Smooth Corner Studio</a>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="project-hero">
				<div class="project-shell">
					<p class="eyebrow">Films and visual stories</p>
					<h1 class="display-title">Thoughtful films with a human eye.</h1>
					<p class="hero-copy">
						I like films that feel honest, warm and alive. The kind of video that is planned
						properly, but still leaves enough room for real people, quiet details, strange
						little moments and the feeling of being there.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="project-section">
				<div class="project-shell story-grid">
					<h2 class="display-title">A story first approach.</h2>

					<div class="text-stack">
						<p>
							For me, filmmaking starts before the camera comes out. It starts with the feeling:
							what the story should carry, who it is for, where it needs to live and what should
							stay with people after they watch it.
						</p>

						<p>
							The work sits somewhere between documentary, brand film and visual storytelling.
							It is considered and well shaped, but not too polished. I am interested in real
							voices, natural light, texture, rhythm, atmosphere and the small details that make
							a place or person feel specific.
						</p>

						<p>
							That might be a short film for a project, a social piece with a bit more care, a
							brand story, an event film, or a small portrait of a person doing something they
							care about. The goal is always to make something useful, honest and a little more
							memorable than a standard promo video.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="project-section video-section">
				<div class="project-shell">
					<div class="section-heading">
						<p class="eyebrow">Selected films</p>
						<h2 class="display-title">A few stories.</h2>
					</div>

					<div class="video-grid">
						<article class="video-card">
							<button
								class="video-placeholder video-poster"
								type="button"
								data-youtube-id="mKWNz7GBMqY"
								data-youtube-title="Soulty Sisters short film trailer"
								aria-label="Open Soulty Sisters short film trailer"
							>
								<img src="/images/films/soulty-sisters-project.jpg" alt="Soulty Sisters short film trailer" />
							</button>
							<p>
								A film shaped from event footage, still images and raw voice notes, capturing the
								soul of Soulty Sisters: warmth, confidence, community and women finding themselves
								in the water.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="video-card">
							<button
								class="video-placeholder video-poster"
								type="button"
								data-youtube-id="E5s8__E0IkI"
								data-youtube-title="BAYTO short documentary portrait"
								aria-label="Open BAYTO short documentary portrait"
							>
								<img src="/images/films/bayto.jpg" alt="BAYTO short documentary portrait" />
							</button>
							<p>
								A short documentary portrait of home and belonging, filmed in an Aramean village
								where Aramaic (Syriac) is still spoken daily. A quiet story of joy, identity,
								land, language and community.
							</p>
						</article>

						<article class="video-card">
							<button
								class="video-placeholder video-poster"
								type="button"
								data-youtube-id="BUcQZa4VlrQ"
								data-youtube-title="Carers for Land and Sea"
								aria-label="Open Carers for Land and Sea video"
							>
								<img src="/images/films/carers-land-sea.jpg" alt="Carers for Land and Sea video" />
							</button>
							<p>
								A purposeful video for the Department of Primary Industries and Regional Development,
								explaining who DPIRD is, what it does and why its work matters across Western
								Australia.
							</p>
						</article>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="video-modal" id="video-modal" aria-hidden="true">
				<div class="video-modal-card" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Video player">
					<button class="video-modal-close" id="video-modal-close" type="button" aria-label="Close video">×</button>
					<iframe
						id="video-modal-iframe"
						title="Selected film"
						allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
						allowfullscreen
					></iframe>
				</div>
			</div>

			<section class="project-section cta-section">
				<div class="project-shell cta-card">
					<p class="eyebrow">Have something in mind?</p>
					<h2 class="display-title">Let’s shape the story properly.</h2>
					<p class="cta-copy">
						Tell me what you are making, where it needs to live and what kind of feeling you want it to carry.
					</p>
					<a class="button primary" href="/#contact">Start a conversation</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<script>
			const videoPosters = document.querySelectorAll("[data-youtube-id]");
			const videoModal = document.querySelector("#video-modal");
			const videoModalIframe = document.querySelector("#video-modal-iframe");
			const videoModalClose = document.querySelector("#video-modal-close");

			const openVideoModal = (poster) => {
				if (!videoModal || !videoModalIframe) return;
				const videoId = poster.getAttribute("data-youtube-id");
				const videoTitle = poster.getAttribute("data-youtube-title") || "Selected film";
				if (!videoId) return;

				videoModalIframe.src = `https://www.youtube.com/embed/${videoId}?autoplay=1&rel=0&modestbranding=1`;
				videoModalIframe.title = videoTitle;
				videoModal.classList.add("visible");
				videoModal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false");
				videoModalClose?.focus();
			};

			const closeVideoModal = () => {
				if (!videoModal || !videoModalIframe) return;
				videoModal.classList.remove("visible");
				videoModal.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
				videoModalIframe.src = "";
			};

			videoPosters.forEach((poster) => {
				poster.addEventListener("click", () => openVideoModal(poster));
			});

			videoModalClose?.addEventListener("click", closeVideoModal);

			videoModal?.addEventListener("click", (event) => {
				if (event.target === videoModal) {
					closeVideoModal();
				}
			});

			document.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
				if (event.key === "Escape") {
					closeVideoModal();
				}
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	body {
		background: var(--ink);
		color: var(--cream);
	}

	.page-header {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		z-index: 10;
		width: 100%;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 22px clamp(20px, 4vw, 48px);
		background: rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.42);
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.18);
		border-radius: 0 0 68px 68px;
		backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
	}

	.back-link {
		color: var(--sand);
		font-size: 0.84rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	.project-shell {
		width: min(100% - 40px, 1180px);
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.project-hero {
		position: relative;
		isolation: isolate;
		min-height: 86vh;
		display: grid;
		align-content: center;
		padding: 180px 0 96px;
		overflow: hidden;
		border-radius: 0 0 68px 68px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(
				90deg,
				rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.9),
				rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.56) 52%,
				rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.28)
			),
			url("/images/generic-background-5.jpg") center center / cover no-repeat;
	}

	.project-hero .eyebrow,
	.section-heading .eyebrow,
	.cta-card .eyebrow {
		font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.2vw, 1.05rem);
	}

	.project-hero h1 {
		max-width: 980px;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--sand);
		font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 10rem);
		letter-spacing: 0.015em;
		line-height: 0.88;
		padding-left: 0.04em;
		text-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
	}

	.hero-copy {
		max-width: 680px;
		margin: 32px 0 0;
		color: rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.9);
		font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.7vw, 1.35rem);
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.project-section {
		padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 130px) 0;
	}

	.story-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: clamp(32px, 8vw, 100px);
		align-items: start;
	}

	.story-grid h2,
	.section-heading h2,
	.cta-card h2 {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--cream);
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7.5rem);
		letter-spacing: 0.015em;
		line-height: 0.9;
		padding-left: 0.04em;
	}

	.text-stack {
		display: grid;
		gap: 22px;
	}

	.text-stack p,
	.video-card p,
	.cta-card p {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.78);
		font-size: 1.04rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.video-section {
		position: relative;
		isolation: isolate;
		overflow: hidden;
		border-radius: 68px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.5), rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.5)),
			url("/images/generic-background-1.jpg") center / cover no-repeat;
	}

	.section-heading {
		display: grid;
		gap: 14px;
		margin-bottom: clamp(34px, 5vw, 58px);
	}

	.video-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.video-card {
		display: grid;
		gap: 18px;
		padding: 18px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.18);
		border-radius: 28px;
		background: rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.42);
		backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
	}

	.video-placeholder {
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.18);
		border-radius: 20px;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(215, 174, 129, 0.18), transparent 16rem),
			rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.05);
		color: var(--sand);
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		text-align: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.video-poster {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0;
		appearance: none;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.video-poster img,
	.video-image img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		display: block;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: transform 220ms ease, opacity 220ms ease;
	}

	.video-poster:hover img {
		transform: scale(1.025);
		opacity: 0.92;
	}

	.video-modal {
		position: fixed;
		inset: 0;
		z-index: 100;
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		padding: 24px;
		background: rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.78);
		backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
		opacity: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		transition: opacity 180ms ease;
	}

	.video-modal.visible {
		opacity: 1;
		pointer-events: auto;
	}

	.video-modal-card {
		position: relative;
		width: min(calc(100vw - 48px), 1120px);
		aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
		overflow: visible;
		border-radius: 34px;
		background: rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.72);
		box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
	}

	.video-modal-card iframe {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border: 0;
		border-radius: inherit;
	}

	.video-modal-close {
		position: absolute;
		top: -58px;
		right: 0;
		z-index: 2;
		width: 44px;
		height: 44px;
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		border: 1px solid rgba(215, 174, 129, 0.42);
		border-radius: 999px;
		padding: 0;
		color: var(--sand);
		background: rgba(28, 28, 27, 0.64);
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		line-height: 1;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.cta-card {
		display: grid;
		gap: 22px;
		padding: clamp(32px, 6vw, 64px);
		border: 1px solid rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.18);
		border-radius: 42px;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(215, 174, 129, 0.18), transparent 18rem),
			rgba(244, 234, 220, 0.04);
	}

	.cta-card p {
		max-width: 640px;
	}

	.cta-card .cta-copy {
		max-width: none;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.cta-card .button {
		width: fit-content;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}

	@media (max-width: 850px) {
		.page-header {
			padding: 14px 16px;
			border-radius: 0 0 48px 48px;
		}

		.project-hero {
			min-height: auto;
			padding: 170px 0 72px;
			border-radius: 0 0 48px 48px;
		}

		.project-hero h1 {
			font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 18vw, 6.8rem);
		}

		.story-grid,
		.video-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.video-section {
			border-radius: 48px;
		}
		.video-modal {
			padding: 18px;
		}

		.video-modal-card {
			border-radius: 24px;
		}

		.video-modal-close {
			top: -56px;
			right: 0;
		}
		.cta-card .cta-copy {
			white-space: normal;
		}
	}
</style>